title: Average monthly salary in Sweden 2018 , by industry
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Average salary in SEK for 19 number of Industrys.
Industry Financial institutions and insurance companies has the highest Average salary in SEK and Hotels and restaurants has the lowest Average salary in SEK.
There is a difference of 25600.0 between the maximum Industry Financial institutions and insurance companies and minimum Industry Hotels and restaurants.
